script:
1). Would you prefer an aisle seat or a window seat?
Yes, I would.
I'd like to sit next to the aisle. 
I wanted the window.
2). Where did you use to live?
I live in Baltimore.
I lived in Atlanta. 
I'll live in Cleveland.
3). Why should we contract with your firm?
You shouldn't be able to.
I'll sign the contract in the morning.
Our service can't be beat.
